title: Rep. Darin LaHood on Trade
itunes:title: Rep. Darin LaHood on Trade
description:
Guests include Doug Heye, Republican Strategist, Former RNC Communications Director & Former Deputy Chief of Staff, Former House Majority Leader Eric Cantor and Krystal Ball, Democratic Strategist and Rising co-host on Hill TV.

Rep. Darin LaHood (R-IL), Ways and Means Committee member, discusses trade.

Rep. Hakeem Jeffries, (D-NY) discusses impeachment and USMCA.
